Company_Description: Founded in 1977, Abo's Pizza specializes in serving a range of Italian recipes in the entire Denver area. The restaurant offers an assortment of dishes, including appetizers, salads, specialty pizzas, cookies, beverages and desserts. Its list of specialty pizzas include Abo's Supreme, Abo's New York White Pizza, Abo's Meat Pizza, Tomato Pesto Pizza, Maui Waui (Abo's Hawaiian) and Chipotle Buffalo Chicken Pizza, to name a few. Abo's Pizza caters to office lunches, outdoor events, sports banquets, weddings, holiday parties and customer/employee appreciation.

Anthony's Pizza & Pasta serve a variety of appetizers, including garlic bread and Buffalo wings. The chain s restaurants offer a range of desserts and beverages. It provides takeout and delivery services. Anthony's Pizza & Pasta operates more than 20 locations in the United States. In addition, it offers franchising options. The chain s restaurants provide several payment options.

Bambino's Italian Eatery in Colorado Spring, serves Italian cuisine. The restaurant s buffet includes fresh salads, soups, pasta, and Bambino's homemade pizza, stromboli, chicken cacciatore, baked pasta and Italian platters. Bambino's has a sports bar and banquet rooms. It provides amenities that include television and a private party room. The restaurant provides banquet facilities for 50 to 100 people, provides off-site catering and has a full bar.

Beau Jo s Management Company operates six Beau Jo s Pizza locations in Idaho Springs, Denver, Arvada, Littleton, Fort Collins and Evergreen, Colo. The original Beau Jo's started in 1973 in Idaho Springs with only an 18-seat capacity. The location now seats more than 700 and occupies four storefronts on Miner Street. The restaurants serve Colorado-style pizza, which is distinguished by toppings that are piled high and encircled by a honey-slathered crust. Beau Jo's uses more than 32,000 pounds, or 16 tons, of mountain honey annually. Beau Jo s Pizza has been repeatedly voted Denver's best by restaurant critics, and it won the Westwood Readers Choice Award in 2006.

Beaujos Pizza is a full-service restaurant in Colorado that has been in business since 1973. It offers a variety of Colorado-style pizzas. The restaurant s menu includes a variety of appetizers, calzones, sandwiches and pasta dishes. Beaujos Pizza provides a selection of hamburger and sausage combo pies. The restaurant offers a range of motherlode, Cindy s lasagna, tofu and hot chicken skillets for customers. It provides Buffalo wings, Caesar and garlic breads with cheese. Beaujos Pizza also operates an online store that offers T-shirts in various sizes and colors. In addition, it provides gift cards and offers membership opportunities in its birthday club.

Founded in 1973, Beaujos Pizza is a family-style dining facility that serves the residents of Colorado. The restaurant specializes in a selection of appetizers, sandwiches, calzones, soups and pasta dishes. It operates a bar that serves salads with a range of dressings, such as lettuce, mushrooms, peaches, pears, cucumbers, kidney beans and black olives. Beaujos Pizza serves pizzas with several types of toppings, including jalapeno peppers, artichoke hearts, diced tomatoes, roasted red peppers and green chilies. In addition, the restaurant operates a birthday club and offers gift cards of several denominations. Its children s menu includes chicken nuggets and mini corn dogs. Beaujos Pizza also provides tips to prepare pizzas and pies. The restaurant operates a general store that sells shirts and hats.

Founded in 1973, Beau Jo's pizza is one of the most famous food chains in Colorado. It owns and operates over 10 pizza restaurants that specialize in preparing thick-crust pizzas. Its menu also includes a variety of pasta, calzones, sourdough sandwiches and salads. The restaurants use honey as a natural sweetener for its dough and pizza sauce. Additionally, Beau Jo's pizza offers gluten-free and low-carbohydrate food items. The restaurant uses solar- and wind-generated power as electricity sources in its facilities. Its pasta entrees are served in seasoned garlic bread bowls. The restaurants sandwiches are prepared on authentic San Francisco-style sourdough bread with a choice of potato salad or chips. Beau Jo's pizza, with a location in Evergreen, Colo., operates a store that provides gift cards, shirts and hats. It also supports several fundraising efforts for nonprofit organizations.

Founded in 1973, Beau Jo's Colorado Pizza Restaurants is a restaurant chain that specializes in pizzas. It offers a variety of appetizers, such as garlic bread, Buffalo wings, artichoke hearts, chips and salsa, baked-stuffed mushrooms and nachos. The restaurant s menu features lasagna, chicken skillet, chicken penne, omelets, calzones, sandwiches and burgers. Beau Jo's Colorado Pizza Restaurants offers meatballs and Italian chicken, as well as pizzas with a range of toppings, including pepperoni, turkey pepperoni, salami, Italian sausage, bacon, anchovies, hamburger and chicken breast. It maintains locations in cities throughout Colorado, including one in Idaho Springs. The restaurant also manages a club that offers gifts cards of various denominations and provides information on upcoming events. Beau Jo's Colorado Pizza Restaurants additionally manages a store that offers T-shirts and caps for men and women.

Big Bill's New York Pizza is an eating establishment that offers a variety of dishes. The restaurant provides a range of salads, starters, entrees and calzones. It offers garlic knots, breadsticks, and Caesar and tuna salads. Big Bill's New York Pizza also serves baked rigatoni, lasagna, eggplant parmigiana, white chicken breast scampi and stuffed pasta shells. The restaurant provides a selection of desserts, such as homemade New York-style cheesecake and ice cream sandwich. It additionally offers a children s menu that includes sausage and meatballs. Big Bill's New York Pizza provides gift certificates of various denominations. It offers space to host several special events, including receptions, birthdays and holiday parties.

BJ's Restaurant & Brewhouse is a part of BJ's Restaurants, a chain of casual dining restaurants. Its parent company owns and operates more than 60 restaurants in California, Oregon, Colorado, Arizona, Texas, Florida, Ohio, Oklahoma and Nevada. The restaurant s menu features its signature deep-dish pizzas, handcrafted beers, as well as a selection of appetizers, entrees, pasta, sandwiches, specialty salads and desserts, including Pizookie cookies. Its menu includes spinach and artichoke dips, sweet onion strings, chicken tenders, avocado egg rolls, blackened chicken sandwiches and angel hair pasta. It also offers special dishes for children, including spaghetti, pepperoni pizzas with diced tomato toppings and grilled cheese sandwiches. The restaurant provides catering services and has a semiprivate room that accommodates more than 100 people. BJ's Restaurant & Brewhouse operates a branch in Aurora, Colo.

Founded in 1983, Blackjack Pizza is a chain of pizza restaurants. Located in Longmont, Colo., the restaurant offers a variety of pizzas, such as Good Deal, Full House, Mediterranean Chicken, Jackpot, Santa Fe and Western barbecue Chicken, among others. In addition, it provides various toppings, including pepperoni, ground beef, chicken, red onions, black olives, green peppers and mozzarella, to name a few. In 1988, Blackjack Pizza officially became a franchisor using the concept of an owner/operator franchisee at each store location. It operates more than 45 stores in approximately four states.

Boston's The Gourmet Pizza is a dining facility that offers a wide range of Italian dishes. Established in 1998, it is a subsidiary of Boston Pizza. The restaurant offers a variety of pizzas, pastas and sandwiches. It also offers various salads that include chipotle chicken and taco salad. The restaurants serves a variety of desserts, such as Boston cream pie, chocolate brownie addiction, New York cheesecake and hot fudge sundae. It also has a special menu for children that include nuggets and lasagna. Additionally, it also has a bar that serves a variety of cocktails, including martinis, margaritas. It also serves wine and beer. The restaurant is located in Grand Junction, Colo.

Buffalo Restaurant and Bar, founded in 1806, is one of Colorado's most authentic Western dining establishments. The menu offered includes appetizers, buffalo and beef burgers, beer battered fish, southwestern chicken breast, buffalo bolognese, garden vegetable pasta, Mexican favorites, beer and wine and non-alcoholic beverages. Apart from a full-service restaurant, there are several separate dining rooms available for private parties, receptions or business meetings. It also provides dishes, party trays and homemade desserts for off-premise events and box lunches for groups on the run. Buffalo Restaurant and Bar also has a satellite with nine big screens for the customers to enjoy their favorite sporting events while dining or at the bar. The restaurant is located in Idaho Springs, Colo.

Byers General Store is an employee-owned business that offers a range of grocery, pharmacy and natural health products. The company provides various services, including photocopy and fax machines, lottery tickets, money orders, phone cards, photo processing and postage stamps. It maintains natural food and beverage, health and beauty, office and school supply, magazine and book, produce, meat and frozen food departments. The company features various food items, including fruits and vegetables, ham, sausage, bacon, chicken salad, cookies, pizzas, egg biscuits and cheddar cheese. It also offers other food products that include chicken ribs, pasta, cereals, soups, ice cream, green peppers, roast beef and garlic chicken. Byers General Store maintains a location in Byers, Colo.

California Pizza Kitchen, founded in 1985, is a chain of restaurants that offers authentic California-style cuisine. It has more than 200 locations in over 25 U.S. states. With a location in Boulder, Colo., the restaurant serves salads, pasta dishes, soups, sandwiches, desserts and appetizers. Its specialties include chicken and shrimp jambalaya, barbecue chicken chopped salad and shrimp rolls. The restaurant has a bar that offers various beer and wines, such as chardonnays, sparkling wines, merlots and cabernets. It also provides a children s program for schools and organizations that includes restaurant tours and incentive awards for accomplishments in fundraising events. California Pizza Kitchen has an alliance with Kraft Pizza Company, a subsidiary of Kraft Foods, to distribute a line of premium frozen pizzas through supermarkets and other retail outlets.

Carelli's of Boulder is an Italian restaurant, serving lunch and dinner. Its lunch menu includes fried cheese, carpaccio, bruschetta, eggplant stack, calamari, zuppa minestrone, grilled chicken, pepperoni, and a variety of pizza and pasta. The restaurant serves a wide range of red, white and sparkling wines, including bianco, rosso, apuglia, sardegna, frizzante, friuli, veneto, piemonte, marche and umbria. It also offers catering services for events, such as business luncheons, bar and bat mitzvahs, weddings, rehearsal dinners, anniversaries, birthdays and charity events. The restaurant is wheelchair accessible and also has a children s menu. Carelli's of Boulder is open from Monday through Saturday and is located in Boulder, Colo.

Founded in 1977, Chuck E. Cheese's is a chain of restaurants and family entertainment centers that maintains more than 470 locations in the United States and Canada. The chain has been recognized as one of the leading small companies by the Forbes magazine. Its restaurants serve a selection of pizzas, salads, appetizers, desserts and soft drinks. The chain s restaurants offer meal options under the Munch N Play Saver, Fun Saver and Family Saver brands. Its restaurants host birthday parties and special and fundraising events. The chain s entertainment centers provide prizes, arcade-style activities, and family-oriented games and rides. Its entertainment centers also organize a variety of animated stage shows. Chuck E. Cheese's operates Chuck E-Club, which offers discount coupons and reward programs under the Tokens For Grades and Super Savers brands. In addition, the chain provides toys and gift cards. It maintains partnerships with Great Clips, Minute Maid and Hi-C to offer promotional packages. Chuck E. Cheese's is a part of CEC Entertainment, which is a publicly traded company that provides franchising options.

Established in 1977, Chuck E. Cheese's is a restaurant chain, which is a part of CEC Entertainment Inc. It has attained recognition as one of the leaders in the family, food and entertainment industry. Based in Fort Collins, Colo., the restaurant offers a variety of pizzas, salad bars, appetizers, desserts and features musical and comic entertainment by computer controlled robotic characters. Operating over 500 entertainment centers in 48 states across the United States and 6 countries, it offers family oriented games, rides and arcade style activities. The restaurant arranges organizational parties, including day care, youth group, scouts and other such events. It offers nutritional information and food allergy information for various menu items and also hosts organizational, as well as birthday parties and fund raising events.

The store organizes music/comical entertainment consisting of life-size/computer controlled robotic characters as well as family oriented games, rides and arcade style activities. Enzo's Pizza and Italian CafeGreat, real Italian that melts in your mouth! That's how customers describe our menu. The reason our cuisine is so fabulous is because we take the time to prepare everything from scratch, from our pizza and bread to our pasta sauces and key dishes. We offer a wide variety of appetizing dishes with exceptionally great taste that is sure to please the palettes of everyone.Come watch our skilled pizza tossers as they make a variety of specialty pizza's as well as made to order slices. For dinner, start off with one of our beautifully delicious appetizers such as asparagus wraps, caprese skewers, or gorgonzola cheese bruschetta. Then move on to one our expertly crafted pasta, chicken, seafood or veal entrees. If you're planning to dine in, compliment your dinner with one of our beers on draft, a glass of wine, or a mixed drink from our excellent collection of spirits. Finish off the evening with a sinfully delicious homemade dessert or a cup of espresso.Couple all these tasty treats with our warm friendly service and our traditional Mediterranean atmosphere. You cannot ask for a better dining experience, so come and join us tonight.

Fargo s Pizza Company is a restaurant that specializes in a variety of pizzas. It operates a two-storey building with more than 14,000 square feet of dining space. The restaurant has a seating capacity of up to 500 guests. Fargo s Pizza Company has a parking facility that can accommodate over 170 cars. The restaurant has an ambience of the Victorian period with wooden artifacts. It has more than 100 leaded and stained glass pieces of art. Fargo s Pizza Company s cooking area has a tile mural that displays portraits of Fargo and Sophia. The restaurant was opened in 1973.

Fatty s Pizzeria is located in Breckenridge, Colo.

Founded in 1975, Panhandler's Pizza is a restaurant that serves pan-style pizza. The restaurant offers soft drinks, wines and draught beer. It provides toppings that include grilled chicken breasts, fresh mushrooms, red onions, green pepper, olives, tomatoes, spinach and diced garlic. Panhandler's Pizza also serves hot wings and cheese garlic bread. The restaurant offers Chicago-style sausage, ranch bacon and jalapeno bacon burgers. In addition, it provides gift cards under various denominations for special occasions. The restaurant offers discount options, as well as utensils and delivery services. It serves a range of Italian and side salads. Panhandler's Pizza is located in Fort Collins, Colo.

Founded in 1974, Panino's Restaurant is a family-owned and operated restaurant that offers pasta dishes, pizzas, salads and calzones. The restaurant serves appetizers, soups, sandwiches, sides and desserts. It provides chicken wings and tenders, garlic and cheese breads and Italian nachos. Panino's Restaurant also serves beverages, such as lemonade, coffee, iced tea, soda, hot chocolate, milk and juices. The restaurant offers a range of cheesecake, mud pie and ice cream. It provides beef, chicken, steak, seafood and mushroom items. The restaurant offers Panino, which is a sandwich rolled with vegetables, cheese and lean meat. In addition, it provides promotional meal coupons. Panino's Restaurant maintains a location in Colo. Springs, Colo.

Papa John's is one of the world's largest pizza companies that maintains more than 3,000 locations in over 45 U.S. states and nearly 25 international markets. Established in 1984, the company operates and franchises pizza delivery, carryout and dine-in restaurants worldwide. Its restaurants menus include a variety of pizzas along with several side dishes, such as breadsticks, chicken strips and wings, canned drinks and desserts. The restaurants pizzas are made from the blends of wheat flour, cheese, sauces and spices with a choice of meat and vegetable toppings. Papa John's serves thin-crust pizzas with the packets of special seasonings and peppers. The company was recognized by the Restaurants & Institutions magazine with the 2008 Silver Award for Consumers' Choice in Chains in the pizza segment. It supports the Boy Scouts of America, as well as has partnership with Junior Achievement. Papa John's is owned and operated by Papa John's International.

Founded in 1995, Papa Murphy's International is a privately held corporation that operates more than 1,100 restaurants in over 31 U.S. states and Canada. It is one of the world s largest chains that specializes in custom-made pizzas with several toppings, such as cheese, pepperoni, ground beef Canadian bacon and Italian sausage. The chain s restaurants also serve a selection of take 'n' bake menu items that include lasagna, salads, desserts and calzones. Its restaurants trademark dishes include the PAPA'S FAVORITE, Cheese deLITE and BIG MURPHY STUFFED PIZZA. Papa Murphy's International provides franchising opportunities and gift certificates of various denominations. In addition, it operates an online club that provides information on special packages. Through a partnership with Feeding America, the chain supports various fundraising events. It offers online entertainment activities that include quizzes and word games for children. Papa Murphy's International has been recognized as one of the best pizza chains in the United States by the Restaurants and Institutions magazine.

Company_Description: Pasquini's Pizzeria is a casual dining restaurant located in Denver, Colo. Its menu features a choice of appetizers, pizzas, calzones, salads, sandwiches and beverages. Its appetizers include stuffed mushrooms, bruschetta, garlic bread and roast asparagus. The restaurant offers New York- , Bianca- and Sicilian-style pizzas with meat and vegetable toppings. Its salads are available with Italian and ranch dressings. Pasquini's Pizzeria also features a full-service bar that serves a collection of beer and wines. Its wine list features merlot, chardonnay, zinfandel, pinot grigio and cabernet blends. Established in 1986, Pasquini's Pizzeria also provides catering packages that include box lunches, deli trays and dessert platters. The restaurant s interior features painted chairs and mosaic tables.

Pasquini s Pizzeria was established in 1986 with a loan of $300 and 1,000 business cards that said, Present this card and receive one free slice of pizza at Pasquini s Pizzeria. Many of the elements of today s Pasquini s were born out of financial necessity, including mismatched plates, mosaic tables and wood chairs. Its interior also features artifacts from local artists. Pasquini s Pizzeria is a casual restaurant that specializes in providing Italian cuisine. Its menu includes a variety of appetizers, salads, pizzas, pasta, calzones, sandwiches, desserts and a selection of beverages. It offers pasta options, such as spaghetti, penne, pesto penne, vegetarian lasagna, eggplant parmesan, chicken parmesan dinner, stuffed shells and walnut spinach ricotta ravioli. Pasquini s Pizzeria offers coupons and specials throughout the year. It provides catering services for private parties and meetings. The restaurant has several locations in Denver.

Call us today!

Company_Description: Established in 1977, Santeramo's Pizza is an Italian restaurant that specializes in New York-style pizza. It serves small, medium and large pizzas with various toppings, such as salami, pepperoni, beef, sausage, meatballs, grilled chicken, bacon, onions, pineapple, jalapenos, black olives, spinach, green peppers, mushrooms, tomatoes and chili strips. The restaurant offers garlic bread, chicken breast, calzones, spaghetti noodles, sausage and meatball sandwiches, desserts and French fries. Santeramo's Pizza also provides a variety of beverages, including beer and aerated drinks. It provides catering service for various events and parties. The restaurant additionally offers food delivery services. Santeramo's Pizza is located in Arvada, Colo.

Welcome to Saucy Noodle For over four decades the Saucy Noodle Restaurante has been a Denver landmark at the same location at 727 South University Boulevard. The little spot, known to locals throughout the Washington Park, Cherry Creek and Bonnie Brae districts was originally known as Jim Sano's when it was purchased by the Badis family in 1964. Sam Badis, a former Big Band Leader and Denver entrepreneur, held court with a gregarious smile and warm welcome and served up what is arguably the best pizza and pasta in town. Traveling the country in the '60's and 70's Sam would frequently buy unique antiques in small towns and haul them back to the Saucy Noodle to adorn the restaurant's, now famous, red velvet walls. When the family adopted a new name for their thriving business ; The Saucy Noodle, they added the restaurant's trademark red and white canopy and adopted a slogan that lives on: 'If you don't like garlicgo home!' The family restaurant became home for family, friends and local celebrities, who frequented the Saucy Noodle seven nights a week. More often than not, the 'Noodle, ' as it is sometimes affectionately called, also played host to international celebrities visiting the Mile High City. As the Badis family grew with children and grandchildren, they too became a part of the fabric that is the Saucy Noodle. When it was time for Sam Badis to pass on the baton, he did so with pride, naming granddaughter Erin and her husband Nathan Markham to carry on the tradition. Erin and Nathan Markham acquired the Saucy Noodle Restaurante, expanded the space to double its size and carry on the family tradition while serving up a menu of favorite Italian dishes from original recipes. On most evening's you'll find Erin, Nathan and their family holding court in grandpa's little restaurant, welcoming guests, managing quality and service and preparing their next little restaurateurs to carry on.

Founded in 2002, The Secret Stash is a food court that serves a range of snacks. The restaurant offers pizzas with a variety of toppings, such as olives, cheese, red onions, tomatoes, barbeque sauce, bacon, sour cream, black beans, roast red peppers, lettuce, pickles, pine nuts and jalapenos. The Secret Stash also offers garlic bread, wings and a variety of salads. It provides a range of drinks, including margaritas, tequilas, coffee, martinis, vodka, shakes, smoothies, iced tea and sodas. The restaurant operates a store that offers clothes, gift items and books. Located in Crested Butte, Colo., The Secret Stash maintains a lounge.

Serioz Denver Style Pizzeria offers dining options and serves a variety of food items for lunch and dinner. Its menu includes smoked trout, Italian meat, soups, and Caesar and spinach salads. The restaurant serves pizzas with a variety of toppings, such as mushrooms, black olives, red onions, green peppers, tomatoes, meatballs, bacon, chicken and roast garlic. Serioz Denver Style Pizzeria offers various desserts, including cheesecake and chocolate and carrot cakes. It offers a kid s menu that includes chocolate milk, macaroni and cheese, sodas and turkey and ham sandwiches. The restaurant also provides a range of catering services for various events and parties. Serioz Denver Style Pizzeria is located in Denver.

Taco Bell is a chain of Mexican-style restaurants that serves a variety of food items and beverages. Its menu features a selection of tacos, burritos, gorditas, quesadillas, chalupas, taquitos, nachos and various platters. Taco Bell also offers specialty items, such as the Crunchwrap Supreme, as well as a special menu for children. It serves more than 2 billion consumers annually through over 5,500 restaurants in the United States. In addition to nearly 250 overseas locations, Taco Bell operates free-standing units and quick-service kiosks at shopping malls and airports. Most of its restaurants are owned and operated by independent franchisees. It has restaurants in Canada, Guam, Aruba, the Dominican Republic, Chile, Costa Rica, Guatemala, Puerto Rico, Ecuador and the Philippines. Taco Bell serves community youths through the Taco Bell Foundation for Teens. Its holding company, Taco Bell Corporation, was founded in 1962 and is a wholly owned subsidiary of Yum! Brands. Taco Bell Corporation employs more than 143,000 people and generates sales revenue of over $1.8 billion through company-owned and nearly $4.4 billion through franchised restaurants.

Located in Snowmass Village, Colo., Taster's is a food services retailer. The restaurant offers a selection of mouth watering, traditional and gourmet pizzas, cheesy sandwiches and stromboli, to name a few. Additionally, it serves a variety of fresh salads, pastas, appetizers, deli subs, calzones, hot subs and many more. The restaurant also serves ham, chicken philly, meat lasagna, buffalo/barbecue wings, pizza roll and chicken fingers, among others. Taster's offers services to areas, such as Snowmass and Aspen.

Uno Chicago Grill is a full-service restaurant that serves ribs, seafood, burgers, steaks, pasta dishes, appetizers, desserts and Chicago Original Deep Dish Pizza. With a location in Denver, the restaurant s list of drinks features more than 10 wines and various specialty drinks, including frozen, mixed and nonalcoholic options. It offers various appetizers, such as chicken thumbs, The Chi-Town Tasting Plate, buffalo wings and buffalo bites. Established in 1943, the restaurant offers deep-dish pizzas, including Numero Uno, Shroom, Spinoccoli, Bianco, Prima Pepperoni and Farmer s Market. Uno Chicago Grill also serves veggie and Philly burgers, as well as crispy chipotle chicken and grilled chicken sandwiches. It is a part of Uno Restaurant Holdings Corporation, which franchises and operates more than 200 restaurants.

Vendettas Italian Restaurant is an eating establishment that provides a range of food services. Founded in 1983, it features a dining room, bar and lounge and serves varieties of pizza. The restaurant specializes in Italian cuisine and offers chicken breast, seafood, roast salmon, garlic bread, steaks, pasta dishes, soups, salads, meatballs and sandwiches. Vendettas Italian Restaurant also hosts business dinners and birthday parties. It provides sausage, grilled salmon, hamburgers, chicken enchiladas and various pizza toppings. In addition, the restaurant s wine list includes Chianti, cabernet sauvignon, zinfandel, shiraz, pinot noir, merlot, sauvignon blanc and chardonnay. Vendettas Italian Restaurant organizes DJ shows and operates in Vail in Colorado.

Established in 1997, White House Pizza is a food destination that serves a variety of lunch and dinner items. Its menu includes soups, pasta dishes, salads, pizzas and sandwiches. The restaurant serves a range of beverages, such as coffee, milk, tea, juices, beers and wines. White House Pizza s menu also includes grilled chicken, eggplant cutlets, breaded tenderloins, bacon strips, smoked ribs and bacon strips. The restaurant s takeaway menu features starters, pizza sauces and desserts. It hosts business lunches, meetings, company picnics, parties and rehearsal dinners. White House Pizza s organizes live musical performances by several artists, as well as offers catering solutions.
